                        <msItem xml:id="ms_i7">
                            <locus from="99r"/>
                            <title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT2126OntheG">Sǝmʿu la-ʿābiy mamhǝr kǝbur Yoḥannǝs ʾAfa Warq yǝnaggǝr
          sǝbḥatā wa-kǝbrā la-zātti beta krǝstiyān...</title>
                            <textLang mainLang="gez"/>
                            <incipit xml:lang="gez">ስምዑ፡  ለዓቢይ፡ መምህር፡ ክቡር፡ ዮሐንስ፡ አፈ፡ ወርቅ፡ ይነግር፡ ስብሐታ፡ ወክብራ፡ ወዕበያ፡ ለዛቲ፡ በተ፡ ክርስተያን። </incipit>
                        </msItem>
                        
                        <msItem xml:id="ms_i8">
                            <locus from="100r"/>
                            <title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT4018Mashafa#Introduction2">Maṣḥafa faws manfasāwi (Anonymous): Introduction, chapter 2: ካልእ፡ ጾታ፡ መጽሐፍ፡</title>
                            <textLang mainLang="gez"/>
                            <incipit xml:lang="gez">ካልእኒ፡ ጾታ፡ መጽሐፍ፡ 
                                እስመ፡ እግዚአብሔር፡ ልዑል፡ ዝክሩ፡ ወፍጻሜ፡ ኂሩቱ፡ ወቅድስናሁ፡ ወሠናይቱ፡ ወአሠንዮቱ፡ ውስተ፡ ዝንቱ፡ መጽሐፍ፡</incipit>
                        </msItem>
                        
                        <msItem xml:id="ms_i9">
                            <locus from="104r"/>
                            <title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT4018Mashafa#Introduction3">Maṣḥafa faws manfasāwi (Anonymous): no id Introduction3</title>
                            <textLang mainLang="gez"/>
                            <incipit xml:lang="gez">ነገር፡ ዘከመ፡ እፎ፡ ይደሉ፡ ለዓቃቤ፡ ሥራይ፡ አእምሮ፡</incipit>
                        </msItem>
                        
